{"tid":26040,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n件覺得自己最英勇嘅事","createTime":"2016-12-06T13:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T11:56:04.000Z","uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"14573a21efe92d12aec304fac36258741655bba1","tid":26040,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"嗰陣好細個，大約小學3,4年班，又細粒又瘦。<br />\n有一次同啊媽去街市買餸，好記得我係發緊脾氣，所以我離我啊媽3,4個身位跟住佢。之後有個啊伯迎面而黎，啊媽行左嘅時候，咁啱佢又行右，啊媽行右佢又行左，之後佢特登撞開我啊媽，繼續向前行，好彩我啊媽撐住咗牆，冇撞跌到，之後我唔知點解好大膽，好大力一鳩撞到個啊伯爭啲跌落地，個心幫咗啊媽報仇而好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:純粹拋舊磚，可能你地唔覺英勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf939677f9584f342afb6bbcb0b3781ce7268891","tid":26040,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:12:59.000Z","msg":"返工拒絕ot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dca60ae6f8500aa790f012b0b4b5ed406b8c63","tid":26040,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1771e37ebd28afb1ef37c84370084d51740ae82","tid":26040,"uid":26102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"小學個時 <br />\n鍾意個女仔喊緊<br />\n因為同我寫紙仔<br />\n而紙仔上面有粗口<br />\n老師話要打家長<br />\n最後我頂左話我做既<br />\n但我又沒後悔喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b1fcab540f25ebff5109513ffa3972ccb71309","tid":26040,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"比十幾個叉仔跟蹤都走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"